e reader should do — once, in the fewest words.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": 18038,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/deep-skill-workflow-required.md\",\n          \"title\": \"DEEP SKILLS — Use the Workflow, Never Hand-Roll\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: rule applies — Never Hand-Roll\\\" | Prioritize when: Never Hand-Roll\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": 16266,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/regression-baseline-and-delta.md\",\n          \"title\": \"Baseline Before No-Regressions; Report the Delta\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: rule applies — never a grep narrowed to your own files — and report the delta in the form `baseline N failing {…} → now M: {…}`. | Prioritize when: never re-renders, a screenshot of the wrong screen, a fixture older than your work making a green result suspect. \\\"No r…\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": 16265,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/main-branch-direct-push.md\",\n          \"title\": \"Main Branch — Owner's AIs Push Directly\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: rule applies — Do NOT default to a feature-branch + PR flow, do NOT re-ask whether to use a PR, and do NOT flag the bypass or the unsi… | Prioritize when: only (the tree often has concurrent parallel-session work + daemon metadata churn — NEVER `git add -A` blindly; use exp…\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": 16264,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/gate-tool-routing.md\",\n          \"title\": \"TOOL ROUTING - Search & Retrieval Decision Tree\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: TOOL ROUTING - Search & Retrieval Decision Tree | Prioritize when: task context aligns with \\\"TOOL ROUTING - Search & Retrieval Decision Tree\\\"\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": 16263,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/finding-is-a-hypothesis.md\",\n          \"title\": \"A Finding Is a Hypothesis Until You Open the Cited Code\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: rule applies — never ground truth. | Prioritize when: only verdict discipline still holds: never soften an active blocker without new evidence.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": 15815,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/regression-baseline-and-delta.md\",\n          \"title\": \"Baseline Before No-Regressions; Report the Delta\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: rule applies — never a grep narrowed to your own files — and report the delta in the form `baseline N failing {…} → now M: {…}`. | Prioritize when: never re-renders, a screenshot of the wrong screen, a fixture older than your work making a green result suspect. \\\"No r…\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"triggered\": [\n        {\n          \"memory_id\": 1745,\n          \"spec_folder\": \"skilled-agent-orchestration/z_archive/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/010-root-level-review-research-convention\",\n          \"title\": \"...ed-agent-orchestration/042-sk-deep-research-review-improvement-2/010-root-level-review-research-convention/checklist]\",\n          \"matched_phrases\": [\n            \"agent\",\n            \"orchestration\",\n            \"deep\",\n            \"research\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"memory_id\": 8109,\n          \"spec_folder\": \"system-spec-kit/z_archive/022-hybrid-rag-fusion/013-agents-alignment\",\n          \"title\": \"013 — Agent Alignment: Runtime Lineage Truth [system-spec-kit/022-hybrid-rag-fusion/013-agents-alignment/spec]\",\n          \"matched_phrases\": [\n            \"agent\",\n            \"lineage\",\n            \"spec\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"memory_id\": 7282,\n          \"spec_folder\": \"system-spec-kit/z_archive/013-memory-overhaul-and-agent-upgrade-release/002-skill-speckit-alignment\",\n          \"title\": \"Task [system-spec-kit/z_archive/013-memory-overhaul-and-agent-upgrade-release/task-02-skill-speckit-alignment/spec]\",\n          \"matched_phrases\": [\n            \"skill\",\n            \"references\",\n            \"spec\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"memory_id\": 1686,\n          \"spec_folder\": \"skilled-agent-orchestration/z_archive/041-sk-recursive-agent-loop/011-sk-agent-improver-advisor-readme-sync\",\n          \"title\": \"Spec: Skill [skilled-agent-orchestration/041-sk-recursive-agent-loop/011-sk-agent-improver-advisor-readme-sync/spec]\",\n          \"matched_phrases\": [\n            \"spec\",\n            \"skill\",\n            \"agent\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"memory_id\": 1675,\n          \"spec_folder\": \"skilled-agent-orchestration/z_archive/041-sk-recursive-agent-loop/009-sk-agent-improver-self-test\",\n          \"title\": \"Spec: Agent-Improver [skilled-agent-orchestration/041-sk-recursive-agent-loop/009-sk-agent-improver-self-test/spec]\",\n          \"matched_phrases\": [\n            \"spec\",\n            \"agent\",\n            \"009\"\n          ]\n        }\n      ],\n      \"surfaced_at\": \"2026-06-26T15:41:25.486Z\",\n      \"latencyMs\": 1844\n    },\n    \"tokenBudget\": 3500\n  }\n}","metadata":{"truncated":false},"title":"","time":{"start":1782488483539,"end":1782488485689}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_0c27c7e061c06f99016a3e9d9c95388191bc2f2559c81aab89"}},"id":"prt_f0497abc5001Cah0U8SkMcmdHR","sessionID":"ses_0fb69c455ffeP1OgZTdo3RBP1U","messageID":"msg_f0497654d001Av6Uw9NZC7kfPW"}}
