{"type":"text","timestamp":1782488645782,"sessionID":"ses_0fb69c455ffeP1OgZTdo3RBP1U","part":{"id":"prt_f0499feb2001Kj4BGhWnltvY6K","messageID":"msg_f0499cb940019w2189uIIEocwu","sessionID":"ses_0fb69c455ffeP1OgZTdo3RBP1U","type":"text","text":"Current-state inspection is next: I’m inventorying mode references/assets and reading the high-signal corpus files behind the prior gap list, then I’ll externalize iteration findings and converge once the per-mode matrix is evidence-complete.","time":{"start":1782488628914,"end":1782488645774},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_091f3a711c53dc74016a3e9e34e0988191adf4c27e7241fcb5","phase":"commentary"}}}}
