{"type":"text","timestamp":1782489060595,"sessionID":"ses_0fb69c455ffeP1OgZTdo3RBP1U","part":{"id":"prt_f04a062d60016G4yxD9SbN4O2h","messageID":"msg_f04a04a1d001A5i7oCYpXuien4","sessionID":"ses_0fb69c455ffeP1OgZTdo3RBP1U","type":"text","text":"The lineage directory only contains an empty `.executor-state/`, so this is a fresh lineage packet. Next I’m gathering source evidence and current mode inventories before creating state and synthesis artifacts.","time":{"start":1782489047766,"end":1782489060593},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0350e70dbecf45a5016a3e9fd7ab1c8197980adc7696a64bfc","phase":"commentary"}}}}
