undations/SKILL.md:269] |\n+| `design-motion` | 5 references, 0 assets | [SOURCE: .opencode/skills/sk-design/design-motion/SKILL.md:289] |\n+| `design-audit` | 5 references, 0 assets | [SOURCE: .opencode/skills/sk-design/design-audit/SKILL.md:312] |\n+| `design-md-generator` | 8 core reference docs, example studies, 2 assets | [SOURCE: .opencode/skills/sk-design/design-md-generator/SKILL.md:86] |\n+\n+## Prior Research Inputs\n+\n+- `001-corpus-research/research/research.md`: taxonomy and structural synthesis, used as a boundary so this lineage did not reopen architecture.\n+- `001-corpus-research/research/gap-analysis.md`: severity seed and validated content-gap map.\n+- `009-reference-asset-expansion/spec.md`: phase scope and success criteria.\n+\n+## External Corpus Sources Used\n+\n+| Source | Used For |\n+|---|---|\n+| `external/taste-skill.md` | dials, anti-default discipline, preflight, redesign intake, copy/mock-data, image strategy |\n+| `external/gpt-tasteskill.md` | AIDA/gapless bento/preflight as optional high-variance landing-page evidence |\n+| `external/colorize.md` | Brand-vs-Product color register, strategic color, data-viz color |\n+| `external/layout.md` | spacing scale, rhythm, container queries, density/structure params |\n+| `external/adapt.md` | responsive/context adaptation matrix |\n+| `external/interaction-design.md` | interaction pattern inventory |\n+| `external/animate.md` | Brand/Product motion register, timing/easing/materials, reduced motion |\n+| `external/mastering-animate-presence.md` | AnimatePresence audit rules |\n+| `external/fixing-motion-performance.md` | motion performance failure rules |\n+| `external/audit.md` | five-dimension score and severity report contract |\n+| `external/critique.md` | evidence capture and two-assessment critique model |\n+| `external/fixing-accessibility.md` | accessibility priority and quick-fix snippets |\n+| `external/harden.md` | production edge-case and i18n hardening matrix |\n+| `external/sti